Class SingleList

  • java.lang.Object
    • SingleList

  • public class SingleList
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains head(Node) and tail(Node) fields for creating a Single Linked List also contains add(Food), remove(Food) and search(Food) methods to add a food item, to remove a food item and to search for a particular food item into the Single Linked List
    Author:
    Sanchita Kanade
